    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Representations, particularly of two-dimensional art, other images, objects, or visual spaces, utilizing raised lines and surface textures to represent the visual image; typically intended for the visually impaired.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
